<section class="text-block">
    <h3 class="text-block_title">Overview</h3>
    <p class="text-block_role">Role: Discovery, Branding, UI Design, Web Design</p>
    <p class="text-block_copy">I entered <a href="http://phillycodefest.com/" target="_blank">Philly Codefest</a> as the sole designer on a team of four. We had 36 hours to create something innovative. During that time, we were to design, prototype, and produce as much as we could. I came up with the idea to create a mobile app around the soon-to-be launched Indego bike-share program in Philly. We wanted to create an app for Philadelphia residents and vistors that would provide them with more than just directions to bike docks and available bikes. We wanted to make Indego not only functional, but fun.</p>
</section>

