<section class="text-block">
  <h3 class="text-block_title">Challenge</h3>
  <p class="text-block_copy">Time was our biggest obstacle to overcome. This was the very first hackathon for everyone on our team so we had to come up with ideas quickly and implement them on the spot. It forced me, as the sole designer, to skip the high fidelty and sketch out as many screens as I could so the developers could start building it out.</p>
</section>

